Anticipated spec changes
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Depending on the result of &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/whatwg/url/issues/599"&gt;https://github.com/whatwg/url/issues/599&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/whatwg/url/issues/599"&gt;https://github.com/whatwg/url/issues/599&lt;/a&gt;&gt;, file:// URLs may either &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;change to follow the same behavior of disallowing spaces, or (more &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;likely) change to be treated as having opaque hostnames which would &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;permanently allow them to have spaces. Either resolution is compatible &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;with this Intent since we are not changing the behavior for file:// URLs. &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;pre style="margin: 0em;"&gt;
