&gt; Anticipated spec changes
&gt;
&gt; Depending on the result of &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/whatwg/url/issues/599"&gt;https://github.com/whatwg/url/issues/599&lt;/a&gt;,
&gt; file:// URLs may either change to follow the same behavior of disallowing
&gt; spaces, or (more likely) change to be treated as having opaque hostnames
&gt; which would permanently allow them to have spaces. Either resolution is
&gt; compatible with this Intent since we are not changing the behavior for
&gt; file:// URLs.
