&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20241010" rel="nofollow"&gt;Thu, 10 Oct 2024 09:00:32 -0700&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
