&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; specified and are working on WebDriver hooks to emulate posture 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; changes
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; during testing, and added DevTools integration, are more great signs 
